name: PeoriaGuide
0:
”Alexa, open PeoriaGuide”
”Alexa, ask PeoriaGuide what I should see”
”Alexa, ask PeoriaGuide to give me an attraction”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: peoria guide
des: This app will give you the top five things to do and top five attractions in the small central Illinois town of Peoria. Whether you're there on business or have lived there all your life, PeoriaGuide can show you places and things to do you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
